<br>
ok first off... Tallon and vallon are the team pvp servers. Ralloz is the original pvp server. On tallon and vallon you can hit persons 8 lvls below or over you, on ralloz its 4. You can loot one item and money on ralloz, that have been changed on tallon,vallon. On vallon and Tallon you can only loot the money now. On ralloz you can not loot bag or anything in bags, but you can loot inventory too. EXEPT for the things wielded in hands range slot or ammo slot =)<br>
<br>
Playing a warriro on a tema server is not a bad idea at all. I play a warrior and i have a very sucessfull pvp rate. Most times people can escape a warrior, due to the lack of stopping a caster. but if you got good resist stuff, and they stick around, its not to bad beeing a warrior =) the main attack is the bow tho, if they run and you got a good bow, you can get em down =) If you choose to play a warrior. Play a barbarian,troll or ogre. Those races have BASH witch is a 100% disturb of spell casters.<br>
<br>
Warriors get a good natural magicresist. Witch makes em hard to root,mezz etc on higher lvls. I have a MR of 98 with not much effort. Having a high MR naturally you can worry about fire and cold resist. Having high resists is everything on a pvp server, so you have like 2 suits of gear.... PvP gear and PvE gear =) it can be a bugger to change it back and forth alot, but when you finally go pvping , its worth it.<br>
<br>
If you have any questions regarding pvp or races or something like that. write it here and i will be happy to teach,tell you whats up about pvp with warriors =)<br>
<br>
There are alot of items and tricks to be tought when it comes to pvp basicly. IT IS NOT like dueling, and it is fare from fairt most the time. Alot of people come up with tactics from blue servers from duels and such, and on a pvp server it just dosent add up =) Its much diffrent on a pvp server then from duels. But alot more fun if you ask me =)<br>
<br>
